page.title: 19GREENSIDE - HOUSING.
page.content: 1. The materials in my house are wood, glas, brick, clay, slate, stone, felt and concrete. It has a toilet, a sitting room, a dining room, three bedrooms and a passage. My house is a semi-detached house. It has a front and a back garden. My house is a big house. I have a tree in my front garden. Both gardens are quite big. 2. My house is made of bricks and it has a slate roof. It has wooden window frames and glass windows. It used to be a dairy and had a shop. The shop is still there. There are two doors on the front of the house and one on the back. We have six main rooms, there are two bedrooms, a sitting room, a bathroom, a living room and a kitchen. My house is a terraced house and it is no.11. We do not have a garden, instead we have a yard.
